Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:12.24,jp.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ　あれ　ここ　どこでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? I'm sure I was...
