Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Acting Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:20.21,jp.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,代行　すごい血ですよ　死んじゃいますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bleeding like crazy!\NYou'll die like that!
